<p class="heading-desc t-justify">
The <b>Co‑Dx Logix Smart™ COVID‑19 kit</b> is a streamlined, one-step real‑time RT‑PCR test that outperforms traditional assays through its patented Co‑Primers™ technology, reducing false positives and delivering clinical-grade specificity. It quantifies the SARS‑CoV‑2 virus from both upper and lower respiratory specimens—including swabs and sputum—with results interpreted via automated fluorescence detection using FAM reporting. An integrated RNase P internal positive control safeguards sample validation, making the assay suitable for CLIA‑certified laboratories under FDA EUA, as well as for CE‑IVD use in Europe and other global markets.</p>

<p class="heading-desc t-justify">
Analytical validation confirms high sensitivity, with a limit of detection of ~5 copies per reaction, and 100% positive and negative percent agreement in clinical samples when tested across multiple thermocyclers and extraction platforms. It''s designed for easy implementation with standard lab equipment (e.g., Co‑Dx Box, ABI 7500 Fast Dx, KingFisher Flex), and includes all necessary master mix, positive and negative controls—enabling labs to adopt high-throughput molecular testing workflows with confidence.</p>




