<h3 class="heavy-font">
Co‑Dx Logix Smart® SARS‑CoV‑2 (RdRp/E) – Dual-Gene Precision for Reliable COVID‑19 Detection.</h3>
  
</div>

<p class="heading-desc t-justify">
The  <b>Co‑Dx Logix Smart® SARS‑CoV‑2 (RdRp/E) </b> test kit is a clinically validated, CE‑IVD certified real‑time RT‑PCR assay designed for qualitative detection of SARS‑CoV‑2. It targets two genomic regions—<b>RdRp</b> (in Orf1ab) and <b>E gene</b>—to enhance specificity and reduce the likelihood of false negatives. Powered by patented <b>Co‑Primer™ technology</b>, it combines both primer and probe functions in a single molecule to streamline protocol and improve assay robustness.</p>

<p class="heading-desc t-justify">
Optimized for a broad range of clinical sample types—including nasopharyngeal/oropharyngeal swabs, bronchoalveolar lavage, sputum, tracheal aspirates, and saliva—the kit offers a rapid workflow of approximately 90 minutes from extraction to results. It includes ready-to-use master mix, internal RNase P control, and positive/negative controls for reliable performance verification. Compatible with standard qPCR platforms (Co‑Dx Box™, Bio‑Rad CFX96, QuantStudio, etc.), the assay boasts strong inclusivity and no significant cross-reactivity across common respiratory pathogens .</p>




