<h3 class="heavy-font">
ARCTIKO – Precision Cooling for Life-Saving Science.</h3>
  
</div>

<p class="heading-desc t-justify">
<b> ARCTIKO’s</b>  product range covers a comprehensive selection of advanced cold storage solutions designed to meet the diverse needs of the biomedical, pharmaceutical, and laboratory sectors. Their lineup includes:</p>

<p class="heading-desc t-justify">
<b>Ultra-Low Temperature (ULT) Freezers</b></p>

<p class="heading-desc t-justify">
Available in both upright and compact models, ARCTIKO’s ULT freezers offer temperatures down to -86°C, ideal for long-term storage of biological samples, vaccines, and sensitive reagents. These units are engineered for performance, energy efficiency, and reliability under demanding conditions.</p>

<p class="heading-desc t-justify">
<b>Laboratory Freezers & Refrigerators</b></p>

<p class="heading-desc t-justify">
ARCTIKO provides a wide range of +2°C to +8°C refrigerators and -10°C to -25°C freezers suited for daily lab use. These units are available in under-counter, countertop, and upright formats, with models tailored for general lab use, pharmaceutical storage, and research applications.</p>

<p class="heading-desc t-justify">
<b>Blood Bank Refrigerators & Plasma Freezers</b></p>

<p class="heading-desc t-justify">
Designed to meet strict medical standards, these specialized units offer optimal temperature uniformity and safety features, including alarms and data logging, ensuring the integrity of blood products and plasma.</p>

<p class="heading-desc t-justify">
<b>Medical & Pharmacy Refrigerators</b></p>

<p class="heading-desc t-justify">
ARCTIKO''s pharmacy-grade refrigerators are purpose-built to store vaccines, medicines, and temperature-sensitive pharmaceuticals in compliance with WHO, CDC, and GMP guidelines. Glass door and solid door variants are available.</p>

<p class="heading-desc t-justify">
<b>Cryogenic Storage (LN2)</b></p>

<p class="heading-desc t-justify">
For applications requiring storage below -150°C, ARCTIKO offers cryogenic freezers utilizing liquid nitrogen, supporting cell therapy, IVF, and long-term genetic sample preservation.</p>

<p class="heading-desc t-justify">
<b>Combination Units</b></p>

<p class="heading-desc t-justify">
Dual-zone models offer both refrigeration and freezing capabilities in one compact unit, ideal for smaller labs or facilities with space constraints.</p>



<p class="heading-desc t-justify">
Across the board, ARCTIKO integrates digital controls, advanced insulation, low energy consumption, and alarm systems to maintain product safety and operational efficiency. Their range is backed by global certifications and is suitable for everything from hospital labs and biobanks to pharmaceutical R&D environments.</p>




