												<label class="control-label"><i class="fa fa-align-justify label-icon"></i>Overview:</label>
												<p class="heading-desc t-justify">Medicons Max are advanced, high-capacity dissection units built to handle larger tissue volumes with speed and precision. Featuring a reinforced structure and enhanced blade design, they deliver superior homogenization for demanding applications. Ideal for high-throughput labs and bulk sample preparation, Medicons Max offer a secure, flow-efficient solution while maintaining the sterility and convenience of single-use functionality.</p>

