<h3 class="heavy-font">
Fast, Accurate, Fully Automated Molecular Testing.</h3>
  
</div>

<p class="heading-desc t-justify">
The <span class="main-color heavy-font font-20"><b>sSPRT™ System</b></span> by FlashDx is a semi-solid phase, real-time PCR (sSPRT™) based sample-to-answer molecular testing instrument, available in 4T, 8T, or 12T configurations to meet different throughput needs. Offering true near-patient testing capability, it enables rapid, syndromic testing at the point of care. The system supports high-multiplex assays—up to 50 targets per test cartridge—covering respiratory panels, STIs, GBS, GI pathogens, and custom syndromic panels, and has earned CE-IVDR certification for compliance with European IVD standards.</p>

<p class="heading-desc t-justify">
Its operational workflow is designed for ease and efficiency: sample in, result out with just one minute of hands-on time. A touchscreen-guided interface and modular design allow random access of up to 12 cartridges simultaneously. Each assay run—which includes automated sample prep, amplification, and detection—can be completed in approximately one hour. This combination of speed, flexibility, and multiplexed capability makes sSPRT™ a powerful tool for decentralized healthcare settings and clinical environments seeking rapid diagnosis.</p>


