<h3 class="heavy-font">
Co‑Dx Logix Smart® ZDC – Multiplex PCR for Fast, Precise Detection of Zika, Dengue & Chikungunya.</h3>
  
</div>

<p class="heading-desc t-justify">
The <b> Co‑Dx Logix Smart® ZDC</b> kit is a CE‑IVD certified <b>multiplex real-time RT‑PCR assay</b> engineered to simultaneously detect <b>Zika (ZIKV), dengue (DENV types 1–4), and chikungunya (CHIKV)</b> RNA in clinical samples such as serum, plasma, urine, cerebrospinal fluid, and symptomatic/asymptomatic specimens. Using patented <b>Co‑Primer™ technology</b>, the assay amplifies viral genetic targets in a single reaction tube, reducing contamination risk and ensuring high specificity while maintaining a fast turnaround time compared to traditional culture-based methods.</p>

<p class="heading-desc t-justify">
Backed by thorough validation, the kit demonstrated reliable performance across various matrices, delivering </b>limits of detection ranging from ~1×10³ to 1×10⁵ copies/mL</b> depending on sample type. The assay includes an <b>RNase P internal control to confirm sample integrity</b>, as well as positive and negative controls to uphold assay quality. With a user-friendly workflow compatible with 4‑channel qPCR instruments like the Co‑Dx Box™, the ZDC kit provides laboratories and vector-control programs a streamlined, high-performance diagnostic tool for arboviral surveillance.</p>




