<h3 class="heavy-font">Pasteur-plast pipettes</h3>
</div>


<p class="heading-desc t-justify">
Pasteur-plast pipettes render liquid handling simple and safe. Cross-contamination and carry-over simply cannot occur making so tedious clean-ups unnecessary. In addition, there is no risk of glass breakage with the resulting danger of infectious material escaping. The Pasteur-plast pipettes are made of transparent polyethylene.
</p>

<p class="heading-desc t-justify">
They are inert to biological fluids and most acids. The low affinity of the surface reduces the loss of cells and valuable proteins through binding.</p>



