                <td><b>Multiplex Detection</b></td>
                <td>Simultaneously detects SARS-CoV-2, Influenza A, Influenza B, and RSV</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td class="width-40 center-bullet"><i class="fa-custom fa-circle font-8 main-color"></i></td>
                <td><b>Sample Types</b></td>
                <td>Nasopharyngeal, nasal, or throat swabs (UTM, VTM, or saline)</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td class="width-40 center-bullet"><i class="fa-custom fa-circle font-8 main-color"></i></td>
                <td><b>Hands-On Time</b></td>
                <td>Approximately 1 minute per test</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td class="width-40 center-bullet"><i class="fa-custom fa-circle font-8 main-color"></i></td>
                <td><b>Time to Result</b></td>
                <td>Results in under 60 minutes</td>
            </tr>
