    <h3 class="heavy-font">Targeted SARS-CoV-2 Detection — Fast, Accurate, and Automated.</h3>
</div>

<p class="heading-desc t-justify">
The <span class="main-color heavy-font font-20"><b>SARS-CoV-2 Cartridge</b></span> by FlashDx provides rapid, sensitive detection of SARS-CoV-2 using advanced sSPRT™ technology. This single-use cartridge is designed to detect multiple SARS-CoV-2 gene targets, enhancing diagnostic accuracy and reducing the risk of false negatives. Ideal for use in point-of-care and laboratory settings, it enables precise COVID-19 diagnosis from nasopharyngeal, nasal, or throat swabs in under 60 minutes.
</p>

<p class="heading-desc t-justify">
Fully automated on the FlashDx-1000-E system, the SARS-CoV-2 Cartridge requires only one minute of hands-on time. The enclosed, microfluidic cartridge format eliminates contamination risks, while built-in internal controls validate each run''s integrity. With CE-IVDR certification, this cartridge delivers reliable and consistent results where fast and accurate COVID-19 testing is essential.
</p>

