<p class="heading-desc t-justify">VAHTS Maxi Unique Dual Index Primers Set 1 for Illumina (Plate) is a specialized kit for DNA library preparation based on the Illumina sequencers. The VAHTS Universal Adapter for Illumina in the kit is the stubby adapter that can be compatible with various library preparation kits based on the T-A ligation. VAHTS Unique Dual Index Primer for Illumina contains specifically paired Unique Dual Index (UDI). After library preparation, it can achieve two distinct and unrelated index sequences double verification, minimizing index hopping and index misassignment, ensuring that the reads in downstream analysis are nearest to the truth.</p>
<br>
<p class="heading-desc t-justify">This kit includes Universal Adapters and 96 different VAHTS Unique Dual Index Primer for Illumina. All the reagents provided in the kit have undergone rigorous quality control and functional testing to ensure the optimal stability and repeatability of library preparation.</p>

