<p class="heading-desc t-justify">VAHTS Target Capture Universal Blockers and Post-PCR Primer Mix for MGI-DI contains Universal Blockers for MGI-DI and Post-PCR Primer Mix for MGI-DI. Universal Blockers for MGI-DI are universal adapter blocking sequences specifically developed for MGI DNA libraries. The Universal Blockers are applicable for dual-indexed DNA libraries and can prevent concatemerization of library molecules caused by annealing of adapters during hybridization, thus reducing non-specific hybridization and improving the on-target rate of hybridization capture. Post-PCR Primer Mix for MGI-DI contains amplification primers designed for MGI dual-indexed DNA libraries. All the reagents provided in the kit have undergone rigorous quality control and functional testing to ensure the optimal stability and repeatability of the experiment.</p>

